options.content: Fraud Detection Dashboard

targets.rawSql:
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(Account_Receiver))
FROM Grafana.UC04_Results

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(Grafana.UC9.Rekening_ID))
FROM Grafana.UC9
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(Account_Credit_Card_ID)) FROM Grafana.UC6a
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(Account_Credit_Card_ID)) FROM Grafana.UC6b
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Account_Receiver) FROM Grafana.UC04_Results ;
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(Account_Credit_Card_ID)) FROM Grafana.UC6a LIMIT 50
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT(Account_Credit_Card_ID)) FROM Grafana.UC6b
SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Rekening_ID) FROM Grafana.UC9 ;
SELECT SUM(Total_Transaksi) FROM Grafana.UC9 LIMIT 50
SELECT ATM_Trx_Amount, Mobile_Trx_Amount, IBank_Trx_Amount FROM Grafana.UC04_Results
SELECT SUM(Credit_Card_Trx_Amount) FROM Grafana.UC6a LIMIT 50
SELECT SUM(Credit_Card_Trx_Amount) FROM Grafana.UC6b LIMIT 50

SELECT 
    COUNT(DISTINCT Account_Receiver) as "Use Case 04",
    Anomaly_Datetime
FROM Grafana.UC04_Results
GROUP BY Anomaly_Datetime
 ;

SELECT 
    COUNT(DISTINCT Rekening_ID) as "Use Case 09",
    Anomaly_timestamp
FROM Grafana.UC9  
GROUP BY Anomaly_timestamp
 ;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Account_Credit_Card_ID) AS "Use Case 06a", Anomaly_timestamp FROM Grafana.UC6a
GROUP BY Anomaly_timestamp;

SELECT COUNT(DISTINCT Account_Credit_Card_ID) AS "Use Case 06b", Anomaly_timestamp FROM Grafana.UC6b
GROUP BY Anomaly_timestamp;

panels.title: Total Suspected Account Use Case per Time

targets.rawSql:
SELECT 
    COUNT(DISTINCT Account_Receiver) as UC04
FROM Grafana.UC04_Results  
 ;

panels.title: %Fraud Rate by Suspected Account Use Case

targets.rawSql:
SELECT Account_Receiver, ATM_Trx_Amount, Mobile_Trx_Amount, IBank_Trx_Amount
FROM Grafana.UC04_Results
SELECT SUM(Credit_Card_Trx_Amount) FROM Grafana.UC6a LIMIT 50

SELECT 
    SUM(Total_Transaction) as UC04
 
FROM Grafana.UC04_Results 

 ;

SELECT 
    SUM(Total_Transaksi) as UC09

FROM Grafana.UC9  

 ;

SELECT 
    SUM(Credit_Card_Trx_Amount) as UC06a
 
FROM Grafana.UC6a

 ;

SELECT 
    SUM(Credit_Card_Trx_Amount) as UC06b
 
FROM Grafana.UC6b

 ;

panels.title: %Fraud Rate by Transaction Amount Use Case

targets.rawSql:
SELECT SUM(ATM_Trx_Amount + Mobile_Trx_Amount + IBank_Trx_Amount) AS "Use Case 04", 
Anomaly_Datetime
FROM Grafana.UC04_Results 
GROUP BY Anomaly_Datetime

SELECT 
    SUM(Total_Transaksi) as "Use Case 09",
    Anomaly_timestamp
FROM Grafana.UC9
GROUP BY Anomaly_timestamp;

SELECT SUM(Credit_Card_Trx_Amount) AS "Use Case 06a", Anomaly_timestamp FROM Grafana.UC6a 
WHERE Anomaly_timestamp IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY Anomaly_timestamp

SELECT Anomaly_timestamp, SUM(Credit_Card_Trx_Amount) AS "Use Case 06b" FROM Grafana.UC6b
WHERE Anomaly_timestamp IS NOT NULL
GROUP BY Anomaly_timestamp

panels.title: Total Transaction Amount Use Case per Time

targets.rawSql: SELECT SUM(Credit_Card_Trx_Amount) FROM Grafana.UC6b LIMIT 50
SELECT SUM(Total_Transaksi) FROM Grafana.UC9 LIMIT 50
